msgstr "代理切换容差（毫秒）。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:460
msgid "Max failed times:"
msgstr "最大失败次数："

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:460
msgid "How many failed health checks are allowed before the node is treated as unavailable."
msgstr "节点被视为不可用前允许的最大健康检查失败次数。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:466
msgid "Run group health checks only when needed instead of probing on every interval."
msgstr "仅在需要时执行组健康检查，而不是每个周期都探测。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:522
msgid "Predefined rule set lists. Select the ones you want to route through the proxy group."
msgstr "预定义规则集列表。选择需要通过代理组转发的规则。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:542
msgid "Get lists through proxy group:"
msgstr "通过代理组获取列表："

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:543
msgid "If selected, rule set lists will be updated through the proxy group."
msgstr "启用后，规则集列表将通过代理组更新。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/routing.js:568
msgid "Traffic to domains matching this suffix will go through the selected proxy group (example: google.com)."
msgstr "匹配此域名后缀的流量将通过所选代理组（示例：google.com）。"

